				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$RSCUij = \frac{Xij}{{\frac{1}{ni}\sum\limits_{j = 1}^{ni} {Xij} }}$$\end{document}RSCUij=Xij1ni∑j=1niXijwhere, Xij indicates for the frequency of the jth codon for ith amino acid and ni is the number of codons for the ith amino acid (ith codon family).

\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
